No, no, no, not like that.

35:21.696 --> 35:24.930
Marquis. Marquis.

35:40.047 --> 35:42.013
That's it, that's it.

35:42.015 --> 35:43.650
Come on.

35:45.085 --> 35:47.718
Yeah, good boy.
Good boy.

