45:10.751 --> 45:12.551
- Silk rein?
- Yeah.

45:12.553 --> 45:14.186
Okay.

45:14.188 --> 45:16.254
Guy's name was Marquis.

45:18.725 --> 45:21.560
Look alive.
We got happy ears.

45:21.562 --> 45:23.695
Marquis.

45:23.697 --> 45:25.431
Now that you figured
that part out,

45:25.433 --> 45:28.500
you might as well go ahead
and jump in the middle.

45:28.502 --> 45:30.668
All right?
Be on his time.

45:30.670 --> 45:32.670
And remember what I told you
about your shoulders?

45:32.672 --> 45:35.405
You got to loosen up.
You got to loosen up.

45:36.742 --> 45:38.175
- What's up?
- Hey, what's up, homey?

45:38.177 --> 45:39.577
What's up?

45:39.579 --> 45:42.179
That's what I'm talking about!

45:42.181 --> 45:43.748
Hey, all right.

45:47.853 --> 45:49.786
I think so, boss.

45:49.788 --> 45:51.690
I think so.

46:15.813 --> 46:17.814
You turning your back on me?

46:44.240 --> 46:46.709
All right, come on.

47:11.165 --> 47:13.167
Come on, come on.

47:22.308 --> 47:25.344
Come on. Come on!

47:27.781 --> 47:29.747
Stay there.

47:29.749 --> 47:31.351
All right?

47:32.752 --> 47:34.253
Come on.

47:35.488 --> 47:37.624
Come on.

47:44.831 --> 47:47.766
Come on. Come on!

47:58.509 --> 48:00.277
All right.

48:03.681 --> 48:05.447
All right.
Now, just stay there.

48:07.284 --> 48:08.651
That's it.

48:08.653 --> 48:09.918
That's it. Easy.

48:09.920 --> 48:11.388
Good boy.

48:12.422 --> 48:13.724
Come on.

48:17.327 --> 48:19.662
I'm tired, man.

48:19.664 --> 48:21.229
You're tired, too.

48:21.231 --> 48:25.268
So, let's... let's do it.

48:26.536 --> 48:29.171
Come on. Please.

48:30.639 --> 48:32.940
Please stay there.

48:32.942 --> 48:34.742
Please, come on.

48:34.744 --> 48:36.443
Come on, please.

48:36.445 --> 48:39.646
Come on, stay there, man!

48:39.648 --> 48:42.484
Just fucking listen to me!

48:44.586 --> 48:46.520
Do you hear me?!

48:46.522 --> 48:49.923
I'm not gonna hurt you!
You hear me?!

48:49.925 --> 48:52.226
You hear me,
you stupid animal?!

49:43.009 --> 49:44.975
Hey, bud.

51:16.830 --> 51:19.499
Where you going?
Hey, stay here.

51:31.110 --> 51:33.443
Oh, my God.

51:33.445 --> 51:35.112
What a business.

51:35.114 --> 51:37.982
But to really get
his attention,

51:37.984 --> 51:40.183
you got to use your hands.

51:42.420 --> 51:44.690
Attaboy, Coleman.
You're getting it.

51:46.124 --> 51:49.492
The horse needs to feel
you and him are in sync.

51:49.494 --> 51:51.862
Whoa.
Easy, easy, easy, easy, easy.

51:51.864 --> 51:54.096
- Come on, keep going.
- Yeah, man. - All right.

51:54.098 --> 51:56.132
Looking good.

51:56.134 --> 51:58.701
