- Yeah.

52:01.973 --> 52:04.606
But loosen the rein
on his neck.

52:04.608 --> 52:07.042
- Shh.
- That's good. Right there is perfect.

52:07.044 --> 52:10.778
Right there is perfect.
Keep going. Keep going.

52:10.780 --> 52:13.448
- That's it. It's balance.
- There you go, nice and easy.

52:13.450 --> 52:16.618
It's all about balance
and not getting discouraged.

52:16.620 --> 52:18.720
Good job out there.
Way to stick with it.

52:18.722 --> 52:20.455
- Thanks, man.
- Yeah, man.

52:20.457 --> 52:21.956
- Great work, man.
- Thanks.

52:24.160 --> 52:26.094
He thought
I didn't see that shit.

52:26.096 --> 52:27.761
Hey, man, what'd I tell you?

52:27.763 --> 52:29.897
Hips, shoulders,
hips, shoulders, baby.

52:29.899 --> 52:31.465
You still can't fucking dance,

52:31.467 --> 52:33.201
but you might be a cowboy
