53:49.574 --> 53:52.110
What's your problem, man?

53:53.144 --> 53:54.811
Huh?

53:54.813 --> 53:56.678
Trying to get sliced up?

53:56.680 --> 53:58.580
What the fuck
you doing that for?

53:58.582 --> 54:00.783
You better stay there, boy.

54:06.156 --> 54:08.623
Stay away from my gang.

54:08.625 --> 54:10.092
Back to the game.

54:10.094 --> 54:11.759
That's right, motherfucker.

54:11.761 --> 54:13.128
- Lift some weights.
- Get out of here.

54:13.130 --> 54:15.230
Come on, man, keep walking.

55:56.928 --> 55:59.027
That's good.

55:59.029 --> 56:00.429
All right, that's it.

56:00.431 --> 56:02.266
Yeah, why's that?

56:05.202 --> 56:06.837
Hmm?

56:10.407 --> 56:13.108
You know that...

56:13.110 --> 56:16.244
at six months,
