56:41.136 --> 56:42.835
You got to be ready.

56:44.139 --> 56:46.072
Stay in sync with him.

56:46.074 --> 56:47.473
What?

56:47.475 --> 56:50.476
Stay in sync with him.

56:50.478 --> 56:53.412
If you pull back,
he's gonna stop.

56:53.414 --> 56:56.149
If you spur him, he's gonna go.

56:56.151 --> 56:59.151
- Make up your fucking mind.
- That's it. Come on.

57:03.757 --> 57:04.990
<i>That's it.</i>

57:04.992 --> 57:07.759
Now you got it, goddamn it.

57:07.761 --> 57:09.727
There you go.

57:09.729 --> 57:11.262
There you...

57:11.264 --> 57:13.899
Why-why do you spur him?

57:13.901 --> 57:15.766
Why do you spur him?!

57:15.768 --> 57:19.504
Goddamn it, don't pull his head back!

57:35.987 --> 57:39.055
- That's it.
- That's all?

57:39.057 --> 57:41.790
Yeah. I'm not the only one
doing this.

57:41.792 --> 57:44.793
You're gonna have to wait
a week or two.

57:44.795 --> 57:46.897
That's not gonna work.

57:48.833 --> 57:50.099
<i>Coleman,</i>

57:50.101 --> 57:52.434
