you're trying to send him...

57:55.039 --> 57:56.472
to stop or go forward.

57:56.474 --> 57:58.207
That's good.
Now, that's it. Stop.

57:58.209 --> 58:00.909
Now go forward.
Move him forward.

58:00.911 --> 58:03.778
Move him forward!

58:03.780 --> 58:05.880
Now you're getting it.

58:05.882 --> 58:07.782
Now you got it.

58:09.886 --> 58:11.385
Straighten up, cowboy.

58:14.458 --> 58:17.926
Now you got it.
Now you got it.

58:19.128 --> 58:21.095
Goddamn it. Who knew?

58:22.831 --> 58:24.532
I got the touch!
I got it!

58:24.534 --> 58:26.100
That's right, Roman.
You got it.

58:26.102 --> 58:28.134
- You see that?
- Go ahead, now.

58:28.136 --> 58:31.374
I got it.

58:32.407 --> 58:34.243
You following me?

58:39.947 --> 58:41.415
All right.

58:46.087 --> 58:47.953
Go there.

58:47.955 --> 58:49.154
Come on.

58:49.156 --> 58:50.758
What did I tell you?
Go there.

58:52.426 --> 58:55.027
Huh? Hey.

58:55.029 --> 58:57.131
Why you not listening to me?

58:58.999 --> 59:00.833
Give me some space.

59:00.835 --> 59:03.034
That's it.
Give me some space.

59:03.036 --> 59:06.272
<i>Welcome to today's
restorative justice session,</i>

59:06.274 --> 59:08.607
otherwise known
as anger management.

59:08.609 --> 59:11.875
I want to commend you all again

59:11.877 --> 59:14.145
for making
the courageous decision

59:14.147 --> 59:17.147
to understand and address

59:17.149 --> 59:20.984
the harm that you caused
the victims of your crimes.

59:20.986 --> 59:24.054
And welcome to our new
participant, Roman Coleman.

59:24.056 --> 59:27.493
Roman, thank you
for making the choice to come.

59:29.894 --> 59:34.431
Today, our goal is
to experience empathy,

59:34.433 --> 59:37.434
to understand the power
of an apology

59:37.436 --> 59:40.271
and to be open to our faults.

59:45.543 --> 59:47.944
Who would like to start?

59:51.449 --> 59:53.982
Remember, this is a safe space.

59:53.984 --> 59:56.853
You guys have already made
a lot of headway here.

01:00:01.124 --> 01:00:04.659
